Description": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "Glory be to Allah the Supreme balance, Glory be to Allah the Ultimate in gentleness, Glory be to Allah the Goal of devotedness, Glory be to Allah the splendor of the Arsh.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "INSHA-ALLAH COMING SOON", "Urdu": "انشاء اللہ ترجمہ جلد آرہا ہے", "RArabic": "SUBHAANAL LAAHE MAA A’L AL-MEEZAA-NA. SUBHAANAL LAAHE MUNTA-HAL HILME. SUBHAANAL LAAHE MUBLA-GHAR REZA-AA’. SUBHAANAL LAAHE ZEENA-TAL ARSHE.", "ArabicText1": "سُبْحَانَ اللهِ مَاعَلْ اَلْمِیْظَانَ، سُبْحَانَ اللهِ مُنْتَهَ الْحِلْمِ، سُبْحَانَ اللهِ مُبْلَغَرْ رِضَعَا، سُبْحَانَ اللهِ زِیْنَۃَ الْاَرْشِ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign