uence": 4, "EnglishDescription": "Shaikh Tusi recommended to observe fasting on the first nine days of Muharram. On the 10th of Muharram, it is recommended to abstain from eating and drinking up to afternoon (Asr). After that, one may eat a little of the soil of Imam Husain tomb (Khaake Shifa) and break the faaqa.", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Shaikh Tusi ne farmaya keh, Mahe Muharram ke pehle 9 dino mein roza rakhna mustahab hai magar yaum Ashura (10th Muharram) ko asr tak kuchh na khaaye-peeye, asr ke baad thodi se Khaake Shifa se faaqa shikani kare.", "UrduDescription": "شیخ طوسیؒ نے فرمایا : محرم کے پہلے نو دنوں کے روزے رکھنا مستحب ہے مگر یوم عاشورہ کو عصر تک کچھ نہ کھائے پیئے، عصر کے بعد، تھوڑی سی خاکِ شفا سے فاقہ شکنی کرے،سیدؒ نے پورے ماہِ محرم کے روزے رکھنے کی فضیلت لکھی اور فرمایا ہے : اس مہینے کے روزے انسان کو ہر گناہ سے محفوظ رکھتے ہیں۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "Ara